Employed Adults:                          $380-$220 sliding scale*
Students (18-27)/Unemployed:              $300-$140 sliding scale

* The top end of the sliding scale covers all retreat costs. For those unable to meet these costs, we invite you to offer any amount between this and the bottom end of the sliding scale.

Partial scholarships are also available.  While we cannot guarantee scholarships, we do our best to make the retreat accessible to all. Please use the link below to apply.

[Online Scholarship request form]  (https://docs.google.com/a/bluecliffmonastery.org/forms/d/1JDNM23N5KxHlrGnSeD2BUVLYxeS-PozjZr-D8J0voSs/viewform)
